| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4570 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 02be8d21-cdc9-5bc8-9c43-31c73dbe6750"
